 sɩsɩ:Laabáárʊ ki ́feńgi). Ɩgɛ́ɛ bú gɛ Yeésu-dɛ́ɛ sáátɩ Israyɛ́ɛlɩ laadɔ́ɔ-daá. Maárɩkɩ woovu Pétro ɖabata. Ngɛ ɩlɛ́ waayáa yɩ gɛ sɩ ‘’Mebiyaalʊ́’’ ɩdɛ́ɛ wasɩ́ɩḱ áwá-daá. Bʊwɔ́rɔ́ nɛ́,
 Maárɩkɩ na Pɔ́ɔlɩ booyóózi baalá tɩmɛ́rɛ. Bɩɩgɔ́nɩ bʊwɔ́rɔ́ nɛ́ Maárɩkɩ na Pɔ́ɔlɩ booyóózi baalá tɩmɛ́rɛ. (Pɔ́ɔlɩ gɛ ɩrʊ́
 weeni ́ wooboná Yeésu-dɛ́ɛ tɔ́m wɩ́sɩ yaagazalaɖɛ́ fáráńdɩ́, Eerɔɔpɩ ɩráa- vʊ́lʊ́máa-dɛ́ɛ nɛ́)”
 ɩzɔɔlɛ́ɛ yɩ nɛ́’’, káma waabána ɩcɔ́ɔ ɩcʊʊná Yeésu. Ɩdɛcɛ́yɩ akɔ́ɔ-rɔ. Sɩ ɩkʊ́ʊ́rɩ ɩdɛ́ɛ Nji ́i ́la nɛ́ waaŋmáa sɩsɩ : ‘‘Yeésu waadásɩ ɩlá maamááciwá ɖabata ɖʊɖɔ. Amá baaŋmáa
