 wénÿeli ́i ɖɩlá weezuú kɩdɛ́ndɛḿ nɛ́-dɛ́ɛ tɔmɔ́ɔ. Yeésu-rɔ, wenbi ́ Ɩsɔ́ɔ waaɖʊ sɩ ɩlá bɩ mɩ́jɔwʊrɛ-daá nɛ́ bi ́nzuluki ́. Ɩsɔ́ɔ ɩlaazɩ nyána Yeésu!”
